INSERT INTO `job_appliedjobs` VALUES (240, '2010-03-30', 84, 1180, 'I have developed strong organizational and customer service skills. As a Travel coordinator, I organized flights, Accommodation and Conference venues.  Ensures all documents regarding Travel are recorded properly.  My jobs also required extensive interaction with the public.  My work requires a high standard and that one can not repeat mistakes as my entire day to day job or to do list are scheduled on a calendar accordingly to remind me as to when is the next chaos to be done. I have developed ability to work in a fast pace atmosphere and maintained excellent customer relations and developed customer rapport.   Diplomatically resolved customers complaints on as-needed basis and ability to follow instructions well and make decisions with no supervision.   Maintained all record keeping procedures without error and effectively developed telephone communication skills and consistently met quotas.', '\r\nI want a boss that gives me clear direction, says he is there if I need him and lets me get on with my work. I want him/her to keep their promises, be honest about what is going on, and to tell me when I make a mistake right away so that I can fix it right away. I want a clear set of rules to follow, and a clear chain of command to consult. I also want a boss who is fair and impartial to the employees and will allow me to grow in my position, or tell me why I am not growing in the position. \r\n\r\n\r\n', 'I have a Pleasant personality/politeness, loyalty, willingness to work hard, motivation, persistence, tenacity." \r\nMy time management skills are excellent and I''m organized, efficient, and take pride in excelling at my work. \r\nI pride myself on my customer service skills and my ability to resolve what could be difficult situations. \r\n', 'Because I would be an asset to your organization. I''m loyal, tenacious, motivated, and I learn fast. I''m someone who could be very productive very quickly and I would I like a start-up environment where I can really make a difference." ', '', '																																									Private bag 2003\r\n							Rosh Pinah									                 Cell: 0812211679\r\n						        30 March 2010				                                                               \r\n								\r\nThe Recruitment Officer\r\nTourism Company\r\nWindhoek\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDear Sir /Madam\r\n\r\nRe: Application for Employment: Charter co-ordinator\r\n\r\nIn response to your advert on the internet, I hereby wish to apply for the above position.\r\n\r\nMy strong initiative and exceptional organizational skills will enable me to make a substantial contribution to the company. I believe a challenging environment such as this, which will provide me an excellent opportunity to utilize my skills and knowledge. \r\n\r\nPlease find enclosed copy of my resume on your web site and application letter.\r\n\r\n\r\nYours truly,\r\n\r\n\r\nL. Samuel (Ms)\r\n																		', 100, 0, 50, 0, 0, 0, 0);
