INSERT INTO `job_appliedjobs` VALUES (1338, '2010-10-21', 177, 1501, '', '', '', '', '', 'Dear Sir /Madam\r\nI am a highly skilled Logistics and Administrative Services Manager with a strong background in successful business management strategies and innovative operations solutions. I''ve had extensive experience with a broad range of professional and administrative positions and would welcome the opportunity to contribute to your organization’s plans. In addition, with exceptional customer support capabilities, I can offer a level of versatility that can make a real difference to your company.\r\nAccustomed to fast paced environment where deadlines are a priority and handling multiple jobs is a norm, I enjoy challenges and will work hard to achieve your objectives. If you are seeking a qualified and productive individual who looks at challenges as opportunities to earn, then I believe I am the right person for the job.\r\n\r\nI have enclosed my resume for your review, some of my key strength and achievements include:\r\n&#61656;	Extensive experience with large scale in providing high level support building critical business relationships and addressing the long and short term needs of the business.\r\n&#61656;	Results oriented site supervision and provision and project management capabilities including scheduling, staff management, project budgeting, and strategic planning.\r\n&#61656;	Excellent organization, time management and communication skills with flexibility and experience required to adjust to rapidly changing schedules and shifting priorities.\r\n&#61656;	Exceptional professional skills including the ability to complete high-level projects, organize manage, and maintain strict confidentiality.\r\n&#61656;	A hands-on problem solver and critical thinker who can quickly learn new systems with experience in variety of office management software systems including contact management Software, Microsoft office and Lotus Notes.\r\n\r\nMy administrative skills and