INSERT INTO `job_appliedjobs` VALUES (1500, '2010-11-07', 201, 4606, '', '', '', '', '', 'Dear Sir/Madam\r\n\r\nI am writing to you regarding the Digital Sales Manager vacancy as advertised on namcruit.com website on the 2nd November, reference number 0201 and would be most grateful if you consider my application for this position.\r\n\r\nI have been working for Mencap for the last five years as a senior support worker and a team leader. However, I felt my role as a support worker is not developing to bigger responsibilities; thus, I have decided to study for a degree in Accounting because I know this will give me an opportunity to get involved into more and bigger challenges. Therefore, I am seeking to pursue a career in business, and the one in finance is one area in which I would be keen to gain experience. I know that Umuntu Media holds an amazing team of vibrant and hard working individuals that made it possible for the company to progress and transform the business into a fantastic success. I believe that I will fill perfectly within the team because I am a very competitive individual, hard working and I have a great attitude. Further, I am a fast learner and I have a willingness to grow and learn. I am not just a scorekeeper but an enthusiastic and energetic candidate who want to help deliver real business growth and profitability.\r\n\r\nI feel that I am good at working with a wide range of people. During my time at Mencap - England, I dealt with all sorts of people. It was difficult at first because of the nature of the job, but I soon learnt to cope with the pressure. I am being told that I am particularly good at coping with reassuring clients, listening to them and talking to them in clear terms. Further, during my time as a teacher I learnt to handle parents’ complaints, whilst remaining polite at all times. I believe these qualities should enable me to cope under any circumstances; therefore, I am the right candidate who can add value to your organisation because I am a low maintenance and highly productive individual. \r\n\r\nI would like an opportunity to discuss my suitability for this role further at an interview and if I am taken I will be keen to start work immediately.\r\n\r\nPlease find attached a copy of my CV.\r\n\r\nI look forward to hearing from you soon.\r\n\r\nSincerely yours\r\n\r\nLaimy Brown\r\nTel: +44 (0) 778 300 9266\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 100, 0, 50, 0, 0, 0, 0);
