INSERT INTO `job_appliedjobs` VALUES (1689, '2010-11-24', 222, 4833, '', '', '', '', '', 'Dear Sir or Madam,\r\n \r\nI am urgently looking for a job in Namiba and therefore I am sending you my application attached for your consideration. \r\nAs you can see in my CV, I am an Administration employee for Healthcare and Healthservices, but also Nurse and I studied Psychology.\r\nI have collected a lot of experiences on the one hand in Nursing and Caring Services, on the other hand in various areas of public health and administration.\r\nIn all my last jobs I have been able to build on the knowledge and experience I gained in my educational career. If you seek an engaged employee, who ist able to work in a team and has a lot of occupational experiences, I would perfectly fit into this profile.\r\n \r\nEver since, I have been fascinated by the idea of working in an african country, for example in the developement aid. 1997 I have been in Malawi to prove the medical institutions of the country. This was a study in the name of the World Bank and my wish to work in Africa increased. Three years ago I already got a workpermit in Namibia for one year, but in the end I could not go to take this chance because of private reasons. Now I have finally been again in Namibia, just came back and saw you homepage.\r\nI still love Namibia so much and  would very much like to find a job or a project in Africa, rise to this challenge and take the opportunity to give my experiences to other people, and of course, learn more about this lovely continent and its very friendly people (even if it would be only for a limited time, I know about the problems about getting a permit of residence and work).\r\nSo maybe you are interested in my person, I will be back in Namibia for ten days from the 16th of January until the 26th of January, so there would be also a possibility to meet personally.\r\n \r\nI look forward to hearing from you.\r\n \r\nYours faithfully\r\n \r\n \r\nStefanie Prager\r\nBahnhofstr. 30\r\n53123 Bonn\r\nTel.: 0228 90919459\r\n \r\nmailto: Stefanie.Prager@hotmail.de\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
