INSERT INTO `job_appliedjobs` VALUES (2471, '2011-05-12', 326, 2275, 'That would be every single time i took the guest up the hiking trail of the Sundowner Walk and having them listening with delight as i spoke about our beautiful country and the Lodge i worked for. ', 'The best way to make someone understand is by showing them how to do it once or twice and than letting them do it.', 'Like everyone else.', 'I dreaded sitting and not having little or no work at all. Because i always want something to do. One can''t just sit still while the world ushers off.', 'My approachable dimeanor.', 'Furn Tech                                                                                                  \r\n30 Edison STR Southern Ind.                                                                                                                              \r\nP.O Box 80269 Olympia\r\nWindhoek                                                                                                                                   \r\nNamibia                                                                                                                                      \r\n\r\n 11 May 2011                                                                                                                         \r\n\r\nDear Sir/Madam\r\n\r\nSales and Customer Service Agent Ref: Nam recruit\r\n\r\nYour advert for the above mentioned position interest me greatly as I am confident that I have the skills, background and personal attributes to fill this role successfully. Considering the fact that I have training in the Hospitality sector I can offer outstanding service and administrative support.\r\n\r\nWorking as a Front Desk Clerk of an establishment, I have picked up quite a few trades that would come in handy at FurnTech. Trades such as: Greeting & responding to routine inquiries regarding sales, procedures and requests for product details, queries and quotations. Providing routine assistance in filling licence applications. The ability & desire to maintain strict confidentiality regarding fragile business and clientele information. Developing the procurement, supply and distribution of information for an organization or client in support of their needs and objectives.  Knowledge of the computer. Ability to work independently from general instructions & broad work expectations. Ability to work cooperatively as a member of a service orientated team. Knowledge of the procedures and services of the assigned work unit & office practices. Working electronically to check the database should the clients want to pay for the services rendered by operating a computerized point of sale system. Entering & updating of information into the database & general administrative support to the team. Providing friendly service to & maintaining positive relationships with all internal and external clients. Most importantly, skill in communicating & presenting a positive, professional image of the establishment.\r\n\r\nAt the end of the day, the focus is business clients, people, guests that we are dealing with. As someone with excellent communication and customer service skills, strong attention to detail & highly organised, I can be a great asset to Furn Tech.\r\n\r\nI am able to commence employment any time at your convenience.  Should you require further documentation please do not hesitate to ask. I look forward to meeting you to discuss this application at the interview.\r\nNote: I am not continuing with Hospitality due to the fact that I would want to commence studies part time in Communication Science next year and major in Public Relations and or Advertising.\r\n\r\nYours Faithfully\r\nGabriel H Booys \r\n', 0, 0, 0, 4, 0, 0, 0);
