INSERT INTO `job_appliedjobs` VALUES (2707, '2011-06-20', 342, 4860, 'Yes I am a responsible person in that when I agree to do somthing I follow through; I take responsibility for any actions I take and I will live up to any expectations the job confers upon me.', 'Procrastination is one of my worst decisions, however even though I may leave things to the last minute I always manage to complete them on time. Pressure allows me to be at my most creative.', 'I have only worked at one company to date and it has been one of my best experiences.', 'The right work force- people who get the job done; the desire and drive to make it work; as well as commitment and persistence.', 'It depends on whether the lie is a material misrepresentation or not, a blatant lie seeking to mislead another party is morally unacceptable. However a white lie that isn''t detrimental to anyone is no cause for concern.', 'Dupwies Management Services\r\nWINDHOEK\r\n20 June 2011\r\n\r\nRe: Job Application –Debtors/Creditors Reconciliation Clerk\r\nI am Rachel Mundilo a motivated, adaptable and responsible female seeking an entry- level position in an office environment. I am currently enrolled at the University of Namibia in the LLB programme (1st year Bachelor of Laws), after being enrolled in the B.Juris programme during 2010. \r\nPrevious work experience at Microsoft Namibia entailed data base administration and thus I have workable knowledge of all MS office applications, I therefore strongly believe that I am able to fulfil the duties conferred upon me. The experience proved that I am hard working, organised, eager to learn and capable of working under pressure. Although I do not have the relevant experience I am a fast learner and given the opportunity to prove myself I am capable of doing so beyond any expectations. I have a clear, logical mind with a practical approach to problem solving and a drive to see things through to completion. I enjoy working on my own initiative or as part of a team and see myself as a reliable, trustworthy, hardworking and meticulous person.\r\nPlease find attached my CV and supporting documents for your perusal in this regard.\r\nYours Sincerely\r\nMs Rachel Mundilo\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
